snippet.title: Projekt Z: Beyond Order - Exclusive Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Check out action-packed gameplay from Projekt Z: Beyond Order, an upcoming first-person zombie co-op-shooter set in WW2. In Projekt Z: Beyond Order, team up to fight off hordes of undead in an open-world environment set on a deserted island. Projekt Z: Beyond Order will be available in 2024 on PC, Xbox Series X/S, and PlayStation 5.
